==Hindi==
===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''वे''' (ve)

# [[those]] - [[direct]] case only, see below for oblique. (Singular: [[वह]])
#:Example: "वे मकानों [[में]] [[छह]] कमरे हैं" - "In those houses there are six rooms." Literally - "Those houses in six rooms are."
# [[he]] - direct case only, far reference, polite. (If no additional [[respect]] is conveyed, [[वह]] is used)
# [[she]] - direct case only, far reference, polite. (If no additional [[respect]] is conveyed, वह is used)
# [[they]] - direct case only.


====Inflection====
[[Oblique]]: [[उन]]

===See also===
*[[इन]](in) - [[These]], [[him]] and [[her]] (near reference).

